          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030611_GCR_131' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew Phillips' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-phillips" title="Mr Andrew Phillips">Lord Phillips of Sudbury</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            moved Amendment No. 138:
            <q>After Clause 63, insert the following new clause&#x2014;</q>
